Give birth in space
The earth is in danger.
Global warming or collision with a murderous asteroid.
Caravans of space shuttles with earthlings on board go in search of a rescue planet.
To save humanity, a big question arises: how to continue to make our species live in weightlessness or even on a rescue planet?
