Norwegian rakfisk: is it the smelliest fish in the world?
Norway&#39;s five million people enjoy one of the highest standards of living, not just in Europe, but also in the world.
Could the secret of the country&#39;s success have to do with the locals&#39; appetite for extremely smelly fish?
Take advanced cheeses.
Place them in the middle of a pile of wet and dirty football clothes.
Wait a week.
