&quot;People are very stressed, houses are expensive, so is education, that&#39;s why people put it off,&quot; said a young manager.
The other people can have children.
&quot;But for me, it is important to be able to dispose of my money and my time,&quot; says another young man in his twenties.
Both men and women cite careers, stress and the cost of home ownership and education as the reasons preventing them from having children.
So, although the government tries to convince its citizens to have children, when it comes to making babies, Singaporeans themselves have the final say.
What&#39;s private offline is private online
Privacy
According to the Dictionary of the Royal Spanish Academy, it is the quality of the private domain or &quot;the domain of privacy that we can protect from any intrusion&quot;.
What is private for those under 16?
How to apply this definition in daily life and on social networks?
Does he understand the dangers to which he exposes himself by broadcasting events on the Internet that he would certainly not share offline?
The newspaper elPeriódico interviewed five young boys, aged between 10 and 15, frequent users of the web.
