&quot;In other parts of the world, people don&#39;t think about that,&quot; he says.
This is mostly the English-speaking world.
Joseph Dougherty, a La Salle University religion professor who is teaching classes in the Philippines this year, responded quickly when asked if he was aware of the &quot;end of the world&quot; classes being taught here.
