We have a grace from the Pope.
Restall points out that over the years there has been talk of many supposed doomsday dates, and he claims that if nothing happens on December 21, &quot;people will immediately start thinking about the next date&quot; or philosophizing. that December 21 marks the beginning of a 7-year period at the end of which the world will disappear.
